# NoHunger API Flow Analysis

This document outlines the complete flow of APIs from the React frontend to the Express backend in the NoHunger project. All frontend API requests are made using a configured `axios` instance (`api`) with a base URL of `http://localhost:5000/api`.

## 1. Authentication APIs (`/api/auth`)
Handled by [authRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/backend/routes/authRoutes.js) and `authController.js` in the backend.
- **POST `/api/auth/login`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/AdminLogin.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AdminLogin.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Authenticates the admin user and receives a JWT token, which is stored in `localStorage` and attached to subsequent requests via an axios interceptor.
- **POST `/api/auth/register`**
  - **Called from**: *Not actively used in the frontend components* (likely added for backend seed or future expansion).

## 2. Category APIs (`/api/categories`)
Handled by [categoryRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/backend/routes/categoryRoutes.js) and `categoryController.js`.
- **GET `/api/categories`**
  - **Called from**: 
    - [frontend/src/context/UserContext.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/context/UserContext.jsx) (loads all categories on app start for the home page).
    - [frontend/src/pages/AddItem.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AddItem.jsx) (fetches categories for the item creation dropdown).
    - [frontend/src/pages/EditItem.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/EditItem.jsx) (fetches categories for the item edit dropdown).
    - [frontend/src/hooks/usePagination.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/hooks/usePagination.js) (used by [AdminCategory.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AdminCategory.jsx) to fetch paginated lists).
- **POST `/api/categories`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/AddCategory.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AddCategory.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Allows admins to create a new category (supports image upload).
- **PUT `/api/categories/:id`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/components/EditCategoryModal.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/components/EditCategoryModal.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Admin edits an existing category name/image.
- **DELETE `/api/categories/:id`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/AdminCategory.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AdminCategory.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Admin deletes a category.

## 3. Food Items APIs (`/api/foods`)
Handled by [foodRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/backend/routes/foodRoutes.js) and `foodController.js`.
- **GET `/api/foods`**
  - **Called from**: 
    - [frontend/src/context/UserContext.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/context/UserContext.jsx) (fetches foods for the landing page with optional `?category=...&search=...` query attributes).
    - [frontend/src/hooks/usePagination.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/hooks/usePagination.js) (used by [AdminItem.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AdminItem.jsx) for paginated admin table).
- **GET `/api/foods/:id`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/EditItem.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/EditItem.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Fetches data for a specific food item to populate the edit form.
- **POST `/api/foods`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/AddItem.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AddItem.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Admins add a new food item (supports image upload).
- **PUT `/api/foods/:id`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/EditItem.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/EditItem.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Admins update an existing food item.
- **DELETE `/api/foods/:id`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/AdminItem.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AdminItem.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Admins delete a food item.

## 4. Order APIs (`/api/orders`)
Handled by [orderRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/backend/routes/orderRoutes.js) and `orderController.js`.
- **POST `/api/orders`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/Home.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/Home.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Public route used by customers when they submit their cart and place an order.
- **GET `/api/orders`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/hooks/usePagination.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/hooks/usePagination.js) (used by [AdminBill.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AdminBill.jsx))
  - **Purpose**: Admin fetches all orders (paginated), usually filtered by date.
- **PUT `/api/orders/:id/status`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/AdminBill.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AdminBill.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Admin updates the status of an order (e.g., Pending, Completed).
- **PUT `/api/orders/:id/tax`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/AdminBill.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AdminBill.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Admin toggles whether tax is applied to an order.
- **PUT `/api/orders/:id/discount`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/AdminBill.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AdminBill.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Admin applies a generic admin discount to an order.
- **PUT `/api/orders/:id/bill`**
  - **Called from**: [frontend/src/pages/AdminBill.jsx](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/NoHunger-main/frontend/src/pages/AdminBill.jsx)
  - **Purpose**: Admin multi-stage update for comprehensive bill modifications.
